Models.ViewModels

Class TableElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • Models.ViewModels.TableElement

  • public class TableElement
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds data to be displayed in the rows of a table. Used in classes where the Model of a Resource can't contain all the data that needs to be displayed.
